00:48:39.090 --> 00:48:41.630
Why is it right minus left?

00:48:41.630 --> 00:48:42.770
That's very important.

00:48:42.770 --> 00:48:44.540
Why is it right minus left?

00:48:44.540 --> 00:48:47.230
And that's actually the point
