00:49:25.320 --> 00:49:30.950
That is, when y = - 1,
y + 2 - y ^2 = 0.

00:49:30.950 --> 00:49:36.940
And when y = 2, y
+ 2 - y ^2 = 0.

00:49:36.940 --> 00:49:40.240
And that's not an accident,
that's exactly the geometry of

00:49:40.240 --> 00:49:44.600
the shape that we picked
out there.

00:49:44.600 --> 00:49:46.560
So this is the technique.

00:49:46.560 --> 00:49:51.200
Now, this is a much more
